# Design System -- {{PROJECT_NAME}}

> **3-Layer Token Architecture:** Brand -> Semantic -> Tailwind/CSS
> Change `--brand-hue` once to rebrand the entire application.

---

## Token Architecture Overview

```
Layer 1: Brand Tokens      (raw values -- hue, saturation, font family)
    |
    v
Layer 2: Semantic Tokens    (purpose-based -- primary, danger, surface)
    |
    v
Layer 3: Tailwind / CSS     (utility classes and CSS custom properties)
```

All tokens are defined in `{{GLOBALS_CSS_PATH}}`.

---

## Layer 1: Brand Tokens

| Token | Value | Description |
|-------|-------|-------------|
| `--brand-hue` | {{BRAND_HUE}} | Primary hue (0-360). Change this to rebrand. |
| `--brand-saturation` | {{BRAND_SATURATION}} | Primary saturation (e.g., 70%) |
| `--brand-lightness` | {{BRAND_LIGHTNESS}} | Primary lightness (e.g., 45%) |
| `--brand-font` | {{BRAND_FONT}} | Primary font family |
| `--brand-font-mono` | {{BRAND_FONT_MONO}} | Monospace font family |
| `--brand-radius` | {{BRAND_RADIUS}} | Default border radius |
| `--brand-border-color` | {{BRAND_BORDER_COLOR}} | Default border color |

---

## Layer 2: Semantic Token Mappings

### Surface & Background
| Token | Maps To | Usage |
|-------|---------|-------|
| `--background` | white / brand-950 | Page background |
| `--foreground` | brand-950 / white | Primary text |
| `--card` | white / brand-900 | Card surfaces |
| `--muted` | brand-100 / brand-800 | Muted backgrounds |
| `--muted-foreground` | brand-500 / brand-400 | Secondary text |

### Interactive
| Token | Maps To | Usage |
|-------|---------|-------|
| `--primary` | brand color | Primary buttons, links |
| `--primary-foreground` | white | Text on primary |
| `--secondary` | brand-100 | Secondary buttons |
| `--accent` | brand-100 | Hover states, highlights |
| `--destructive` | red-500 | Delete actions, errors |
| `--ring` | brand color | Focus rings |

### Borders
| Token | Maps To | Usage |
|-------|---------|-------|
| `--border` | brand-200 | Default borders |
| `--input` | brand-200 | Input field borders |

